data.description:
An amazing opportunity to own a patch of heaven in a perfect setting for running a farm, growing crops, starting a homestead, hunting, or just living in a beautiful rural area with plenty of space! This property consists of 2 houses, 3 wells, 1200 sq ft shop, RV carport with septic, water, and electric hook up, multiple cross fences, stunning seasonal creek, 3 stock tanks, additional homesite-RV area with septic and electric, and all with easy access to Blanket, Brownwood, and Comanche. 
The main house, at 2400 sq ft, was beautifully custom built in 2013 and finished out in repurposed wood for an authentic farm house look with solid structure. A beautiful from deck The kitchen in this house is to die for and will clearly impress with its size and attention to detail. The second house, around 1200 sq ft, has 2 bed 2 bath and has been remodeled over the years. Many an artifact have been discovered on this property! This property is a must see for anyone looking for land!
